sequenceDiagram
    participant Net as Network
    participant Fastify as Backend API
    participant S3 as Object Storage (MinIO)
    participant DB as Postgres
    
    Net->>+Fastify: Receive POST /api/site (.tar.gz)
    Fastify->>Fastify: Parse FormData (name + archive)
    Fastify->>DB: Check if project site exists
    alt Site exists
        DB-->>Fastify: Site found
        Fastify->>S3: Delete old S3 files
        Fastify->>DB: Clear old site_files rows
    else Site does not exist
        DB-->>Fastify: Not found
        Fastify->>DB: Create new Site record
    end
    Fastify->>Fastify: Extract archive into individual files
    Fastify->>S3: Upload each file to S3
    Fastify->>DB: Insert site_files record per file
    Fastify-->>-Net: 200/201 (Deployment Success)
